'''WASP-12b'''是由[[超廣角尋找行星|SuperWASP]]使用[[凌_(天體)|凌日法]]於2008年4月1日發現環繞著[[WASP-12|WASP-12]]的一顆[[系外行星|系外行星]]<ref name=wasp />。由於WASP-12b環繞的軌道非常靠近母恆星，它是已知系外行星中密度最低者之一（因為接受母恆星的輻射能而膨脹）。該恆星的軌道周期只比一天略長一點，而地球環繞[[太陽|太陽]]一周要365天。它與母恆星的距離只有[[地球|地球]]與[[太陽|太陽]]距離的<sup>1</sup>/<sub>44</sub>，[[軌道離心率|軌道離心率]]則與木星相同。2013年12月3日，天文學家報告以[[哈伯太空望遠鏡|哈伯太空望遠鏡]]觀測WASP-12b的大氣層時發現了水的存在<ref name="NASA-20131203">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=Hubble Traces Subtle Signals of Water on Hazy Worlds |url=http://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/hubble-traces-subtle-signals-of-water-on-hazy-worlds/ |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |date=3 December 2013 |accessdate=4 December 2013 |archive-date=2019-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830203146/https://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/hubble-traces-subtle-signals-of-water-on-hazy-worlds/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ApJ-20131203">{{cite journal |last1=Mandell |first1=Avi M. |last2=Haynes |first2=Korey |last3=Sinukoff |first3=Evan |last4=Madhusudhan |first4=Nikku |last5=Burrows |first5=Adam |last6=Deming |first6=Drake |title=Exoplanet Transit Spectroscopy Using WFC3: WASP-12 b, WASP-17 b, and WASP-19 b |url=http://iopscience.iop.org/0004-637X/779/2/128/article |date=3 December 2013 |journal=[[天文物理期刊|Astrophysical Journal]] |volume=779 |issue=2 |page=128 |doi=10.1088/0004-637X/779/2/128 |accessdate=4 December 2013 |arxiv = 1310.2949 |bibcode = 2013ApJ...779..128M }}</ref>。2014年7月，NASA宣布在包含WASP-12b的3顆系外行星上偵測到極乾燥大氣層（另外兩顆為[[HD_189733_b|HD 189733 b]]和[[HD_209458_b|HD 209458 b]]）<ref name="NASA-20140724">{{cite web |last=Harrington |first=J.D. |last2=Villard |first2=Ray |title=RELEASE 14-197 - Hubble Finds Three Surprisingly Dry Exoplanets |url=http://www.nasa.gov/press/2014/july/hubble-finds-three-surprisingly-dry-exoplanets/ |date=July 24, 2014 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=July 25, 2014 |archive-date=2017-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610055419/https://www.nasa.gov/press/2014/july/hubble-finds-three-surprisingly-dry-exoplanets/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年9月，天文學家宣布以哈伯太空望遠鏡觀測結果顯示，WASP-12b表面可吸收94%的入射光輻射。因此WASP-12b被形容其外觀有如瀝青一般黑暗，並被稱為「黑色瀝青」熱木星<ref name="DM-20170914">{{cite news |last=Lazzaro |first=Sage |title=Hubble spots a 'pitch black' hot Jupiter planet that Eats light instead of reflecting it |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-4885982/Hubble-spots-pitch-black-planet-hot-eats-light.html |date=14 September 2017 |work=[[每日郵報|Daily Mail]] |accessdate=14 September 2017 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024244/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-4885982/Hubble-spots-pitch-black-planet-hot-eats-light.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Wall |first=Mike |date=18 September 2017 |title=The hellish world WASP-12b is darker than fresh asphalt in visible light, but glows red-hot in infrared |url=https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/astronomers-discover-pitch-black-exoplanet/ |work=[[科学美国人|Scientific American]] |access-date=19 September 2017 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228041507/https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/astronomers-discover-pitch-black-exoplanet/ }}</ref>。

== 特性==
[[File:The Pitch-Black Exoplanet WASP-12b.jpg|thumb|left|200px|
WASP-12b表面吸收94％的照射在其上的光輻射能，導致該行星的[[反照率|反照率]]，即反射光強度與入射光強度比值非常低<ref>{{cite web|title=Hubble observes pitch black planet|url=https://www.spacetelescope.org/news/heic1714/|website=www.spacetelescope.org|accessdate=15 September 2017|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203041526/https://spacetelescope.org/news/heic1714/}}</ref>。]]
這顆行星因為極為靠近WASP-12，所以受到潮汐力的扭曲成為卵形，並且以每年大約10<sup>−7</sup> [[木星質量|M<sub>J</sub>]]的速率將大氣層的氣體剝離<ref>{{Cite journal |first=Shu-lin |last=Li |first2=N. |last2=Miller |first3=Douglas N. C. |last3=Lin |lastauthoramp=yes |first4=Jonathan J. |last4=Fortney |date=2010 |title=WASP-12b as a prolate, inflated and disrupting planet from tidal dissipation |journal=[[自然_(期刊)|Nature]] |volume=463 |issue=7284 |pages=1054–1056 |doi=10.1038/nature08715 |pmid=20182506 |postscript=<!--None--> |bibcode = 2010Natur.463.1054L |arxiv = 1002.4608 }}</ref>。前述就是所謂的「潮汐加熱」，以及WASP-12b與其母恆星極為接近，兩項條件結合起來使WASP-12b表面溫度超過{{convert|2500|K|°C|-2}}。

在2010年5月20日，天文學家以[[哈伯太空望遠鏡|哈伯太空望遠鏡]]觀測結果指出WASP-12b正在被母恆星吞噬。儘管之前科學家已經意識到行星可能被母恆星吞噬，這還是第一次如此明確觀測到這樣的事實。NASA的天文學家預測WASP-12b的壽命剩下約1000萬年<ref name="Hubble observation">[http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hubble/science/planet-eater.html Hubble Finds a Star Eating a Planet] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hubble/science/planet-eater.html |date=20211111124425 }} nasa.gov. 2010-05-20. Retrieved on 2010-12-10.</ref>。

另外，[[北京大學|北京大學]]李抒璘（Shu-lin Li）等人對WASP-12b的使用哈伯太空望遠鏡的[[宇宙起源頻譜儀|宇宙起源頻譜儀]]進行觀測。該次觀測最終確認成果於2009年2月的《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》期刊。WASP-12b的大氣層大幅膨脹至半徑約為木星的3倍，而它的質量只比木星高40%。

=== 碳含量 ===
最近的觀測證據顯示，WASP-12b具有相當高的碳/氧含量比，而且明顯高於太陽，這顯示它是富含碳的氣態巨行星。與觀測值相符合的碳/氧含量比大約為1，而太陽為0.54。碳/氧含量比研究認為富含碳的行星可能在恆星系統內形成<ref name="C-O-ratio">{{Cite journal | last1 = Madhusudhan | first1 = N. | last2 = Harrington | first2 = J. | last3 = Stevenson | first3 = K. B. | last4 = Nymeyer | first4 = S. | last5 = Campo | first5 = C. J. | last6 = Wheatley | first6 = P. J. | last7 = Deming | first7 = D. | last8 = Blecic | first8 = J. | last9 = Hardy | first9 = R. A. | doi = 10.1038/nature09602 | last10 = Lust | first10 = N. B. | last11 = Anderson | first11 = D. R. | last12 = Collier-Cameron | first12 = A. | last13 = Britt | first13 = C. B. T. | last14 = Bowman | first14 = W. C. | last15 = Hebb | first15 = L. | last16 = Hellier | first16 = C. | last17 = Maxted | first17 = P. F. L. | last18 = Pollacco | first18 = D. | last19 = West | first19 = R. G. | title = A high C/O ratio and weak thermal inversion in the atmosphere of exoplanet WASP-12b | journal = Nature | volume = 469 | issue = 7328 | pages = 64–67 | year = 2010 | pmid =  21150901| pmc = |bibcode = 2011Natur.469...64M |arxiv = 1012.1603 }}</ref>。
該研究團隊的其中一位研究人員評論：「當碳含量多於氧時，你將會碰到純碳組成的岩石，如鑽石或石墨。」<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.usnews.com/science/articles/2010/12/10/carbon-rich-planet-a-girls-best-friend.html | title = Carbon-Rich Planet: A Girl's Best Friend? | date = 10 December 2010 | publisher = [[美国新闻与世界报道|U.S. News & World Report]] | access-date = 2018-02-22 | archive-date = 2010-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101215182604/http://www.usnews.com/science/articles/2010/12/10/carbon-rich-planet-a-girls-best-friend.html }}</ref>

一篇已發表的研究論文指出：「即使沒有觀測到像WASP-12b這樣富含碳的具大行星，理論模型仍預測有許多主要由碳組成的固體行星存在。例如可能會有內部成分由石墨或鑽石為主導的行星存在，而地球的岩石主要成分為矽酸鹽<ref name="C-O-ratio"/>。這些主張引起媒體關注<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.thestar.com/article/905303--carbon-rich-planet-could-house-diamonds | title = Carbon-rich planet could house diamonds | author = Lorianna De Giorgio | date = 10 December 2010 | publisher = [[多倫多星報|Toronto Star]] | access-date = 2018-02-22 | archive-date = 2012-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023020822/http://www.thestar.com/article/905303--carbon-rich-planet-could-house-diamonds }}</ref>，部分人士甚至稱WASP-12b為「鑽石行星」<ref>{{cite news | title = Diamond planet found by Keele University astronomers | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/stoke/hi/people_and_places/nature/newsid_9272000/9272801.stm | date = 9 December 2010 | publisher = [[英國廣播公司新聞網|BBC News Online]] | accessdate = 2018-02-22 | archive-date = 2017-08-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170805104459/http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/stoke/hi/people_and_places/nature/newsid_9272000/9272801.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

WASP-12b在大氣層中的碳則以一氧化碳和甲烷的形式存在。這項研究發表在《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》期刊上<ref>{{Cite news|title=Exoplanet Strikes Carbon Pay Dirt|url=http://www.scientificamerican.com/podcast/episode.cfm?id=exoplanet-strikes-carbon-paydirt-10-12-09|newspaper=[[科学美国人|Scientific American]]|date=December 9, 2010|first=Christopher|last=Intagliata|accessdate=2018-02-22|archive-date=2013-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508020705/http://www.scientificamerican.com/podcast/episode.cfm?id=exoplanet-strikes-carbon-paydirt-10-12-09}}</ref>。
